  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的控制流程图。核心是从PLC逻辑单元开始，经过执行器控制器，再到边缘节点。你能先把这个主干画出来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解是从PLC逻辑出发，先到执行器控制器，再到边缘节点。这里PLC逻辑和执行器控制器之间是单向控制关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，单向的。PLC逻辑发出控制指令给执行器控制器。然后执行器控制器把数据推送到边缘节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主干已画好：PLC逻辑 → 执行器控制器 → 边缘节点。接下来边缘节点之后怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "边缘节点这里要做一个判断，需要回到PLC逻辑进行状态校验。这个判断节点用菱形表示，分出两条路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，边缘节点之后连到一个判断节点，这个判断节点还是标记为PLC逻辑吗？然后Yes分支和No分支分别去哪？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，判断节点就是PLC逻辑。Yes分支走遥测数据流，No分支回到另一个边缘节点做本地缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "分支结构已添加：PLC逻辑判断后，Yes到遥测数据流，No到边缘节点。这两个分支之后汇聚到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两个分支都要进入MQTT Broker做消息路由。这里再加一个判断，Yes的话指令回传给执行器控制器形成闭环，No的话走另一个执行器控制器做告警处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，遥测数据流和边缘节点都连到MQTT Broker，然后MQTT Broker判断：Yes回传执行器控制器，No到另一个执行器控制器。我检查一下连线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我发现刚才边缘节点到PLC逻辑的箭头方向需要调整，应该是边缘节点指向PLC逻辑判断节点，而不是双向。已经修正。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "修正得好。现在整个闭环形成了：正常数据走遥测流上云，异常数据本地缓存后经MQTT回传或告警。MQTT Broker的Yes分支回到最初的执行器控制器，确认一下这个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "闭环已确认：MQTT Broker Yes分支连回第一个执行器控制器。整个流程现在从PLC逻辑出发，最终能回到执行器控制器形成控制闭环。还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "PLC逻辑出现了两次，一次是起始节点，一次是判断节点，这个会不会混淆？需要区分一下吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "在实际系统中这确实是同一个PLC逻辑单元，只是功能不同：矩形的是控制发起，菱形的是状态判断。保持同名是合理的，表示同一设备的两个角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "说得通，就这样定稿。完整的工业物联网控制流程：PLC逻辑控制→执行器→边缘节点→状态判断→分流到遥测或缓存→经MQTT路由→闭环控制或告警。",
      "elements_involved": [
